Insider Activity


Individual




George Ward Bodenheimer



Mr. George W. Bodenheimer is on the Board of Directors at Under Armour, Inc., Sirius XM Radio, Inc. and Sirius XM Holdings, Inc. Mr. Bodenheimer was previously employed as Co-Chairman-Media Networks by The Walt Disney Co., President by ABC Sports, Inc., and Executive Chairman by ESPN, Inc. He also served on the board at The Advertising Council, Inc. and The Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Denison University.



